ons:**\n\n*   Large sequences could create large files/strings. Performance shouldn\u0027t be an issue for typical cycle counts (\u003c1000) in JS.\n*   Error handling if sequence is empty.\n*   MIME types for different browsers. Standard ones should work.\n*   Timestamp formatting for filename.",
